    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an ICP (Ideal Customer Profile) scoring agent for AVIAN, a company that sells AI-powered thermal camera systems that detect fire risk and abnormal heat in industrial facilities.\n\nAVIAN's ideal customer profile:\n- Industry: Manufacturing, Chemical Processing, Food & Beverage, Automotive, Energy\n- Company size: 200–5,000 employees\n- Buyer roles: Plant Manager, EHS Director, Maintenance Manager, Safety Officer, Operations VP\n- Pain: Fire risk, thermal runaway, equipment failure, unplanned downtime, OSHA compliance, insurance audits\n- Geography: North America or Europe\n\nHere is the research output for this company:\n{{ $json.output }}\n\nScore this company across these 4 categories (0–25 points each):\n1. Company Fit (industry match, size match, geography)\n2. Role Fit (do they likely have the right buyer personas on staff?)\n3. Pain Fit (how strong is their fire/thermal/safety pain based on the research?)\n4. Timing Fit (are there signals suggesting urgency — recent incidents, audits, expansion, new facilities?)\n\nReturn your response in EXACTLY this format and nothing else:\nCompany Fit: [score]/25 - [one sentence reason]\nRole Fit: [score]/25 - [one sentence reason]\nPain Fit: [score]/25 - [one sentence reason]\nTiming Fit: [score]/25 - [one sentence reason]\nTotal Score: [sum]/100\nICP Tier: [Hot if 70+, Warm if 40-69, Cold if below 40]\nSummary: [2 sentences on why this company is or isn't a strong AVIAN prospect]",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1152,
        128
      ],
      "id": "8d81b5ee-7be9-4983-808c-663993cb1106",
      "name": "ICP Scoring Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a B2B research analyst for AVIAN, a thermal camera fire prevention company.\n\nCompany: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json[\"Company Name\"] }}\nIndustry: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json[\"Industry\"] }}\n\nHere are search results about this company:\n{{ JSON.stringify($input.first().json).slice(0, 1500) || \"Limited data available - provide best estimate based on company name and industry\" }}\n\nRespond in this exact format only - nothing else:\nDESCRIPTION: [one sentence about what the company does]\nEMPLOYEES: [approximate headcount - give a number like \"2,500\" or \"500-1,000\"]\nCOMPANY SIZE: [Small (1-200) / Medium (201-1,000) / Large (1,001-5,000) / Enterprise (5,000+)]\nPAIN SIGNALS: [one sentence about any fire, safety, thermal, or downtime issues]\nPAIN RATING: [High, Medium, or Low]",
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
