    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert B2B outbound copywriter for AVIAN, a company that sells AI-powered thermal camera systems that detect abnormal heat and prevent industrial fires before they start.\n\nAVIAN's value proposition:\n- 24/7 continuous thermal monitoring of industrial facilities\n- AI detects abnormal heat patterns before they become fires\n- Protects assets, reduces insurance premiums, ensures OSHA compliance\n- Prevents costly unplanned downtime from equipment failure\n- Already proven in manufacturing, chemical, food processing, and automotive facilities\n\nHere is the ICP scoring and research for this company:\n{{ $json.output }}\n\nGenerate exactly 3 outreach assets for a Plant Manager or EHS Director at this company:\n\nASSET 1 — COLD EMAIL OPENER (2 sentences max):\nWrite a highly specific opening line for a cold email that references something real about this company's industry, facility type, or pain signals. Do NOT use generic phrases like \"I hope this finds you well\" or \"I wanted to reach out.\" Reference their specific situation.\n\nASSET 2 — LINKEDIN CONNECTION REQUEST (under 300 characters):\nWrite a short, human LinkedIn connection request message. Reference their role and one specific pain point. No fluff.\n\nASSET 3 — PHONE CALL TALKING POINTS (3 bullet points):\nWrite 3 specific talking points for a 2-minute cold call opening. Each bullet should be one sentence and reference AVIAN's value in the context of this company's industry and pain signals.\n\nFormat your response EXACTLY like this:\nEMAIL OPENER: [your email opener here]\nLINKEDIN MESSAGE: [your LinkedIn message here]\nCALL POINT 1: [first talking point]\nCALL POINT 2: [second talking point]\nCALL POINT 3: [third talking point]\n\n{{ $json.failure_reason ? \"REVISION REQUIRED: \" + $json.failure_reason : \"\" }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1792,
        128
      ],
